proceeds from repayments of line of credit
proceeds from repayments of lines of credit

payments for repurchase of common stock

proceeds from sale of property plant and equipment
supplemental assets acquired under capital leases
supplemental noncash or part noncash divestiture amount of consideration received

Sales and Maturities of Investments: proceeds from maturities prepayments and calls of shortterm investments
proceeds from sale of short term investments

increase decrease in accounts and other receivables
